{"tid":601903,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[人渣敗類]有冇人同我一樣好鐘意收割人地既痛苦","createTime":"2018-03-22T14:50:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-24T03:15:10.000Z","uid":32810,"like":14,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"bba5568a2448c6c62f4dd8dc86fd2e6a03992a4d","tid":601903,"uid":32810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T14:50:41.000Z","msg":"見到家破人亡，功敗垂成會好心涼<br />\n每次見到人遇到不幸，或者努力過後毫無收穫，都忍唔住覺得好興奮，甚至主動上網睇人地仆街既實錄(例如叫雞中性病，賭輸錢等，mk妹比mk仔中出即飛瘋狂撚狗等等)，特別係衰on9搞到自己一身蟻果種<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n知道自己好異常好仆街好冇同理心，但改唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇人同我一樣都係呢種陷家鏟黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6158e83dcb3f48c5abf2b181966adcd37273fba","tid":601903,"uid":26474,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T14:51:50.000Z","msg":"他朝君體也相同"},{"pid":"e7b4b2fd009fc3bdec2e2427842311f5461ca48f","tid":601903,"uid":32810,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"f6158e83dcb3f48c5abf2b181966adcd37273fba","tid":601903,"uid":26474,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T14:51:50.000Z","msg":"他朝君體也相同"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T14:53:06.000Z","msg":"我係仆街，我該死<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8adee8120a3be705e18d8d8cc105bab60774d23","tid":601903,"uid":177851,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T14:57:38.000Z","msg":"風水輪流轉"},{"pid":"84a52afae61dfc240fb31d2304efa4f0962f2a54","tid":601903,"uid":32810,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"c8adee8120a3be705e18d8d8cc105bab60774d23","tid":601903,"uid":177851,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T14:57:38.000Z","msg":"風水輪流轉"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T14:58:31.000Z","msg":"睇人仆街最開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14f9f17f80fb0ec14517801b777a319efb2da215","tid":601903,"uid":25221,"like":0,"disli